{"title_page": "Savoie's 3rd constituency", "text_new": "{{short description|Constituency of the French Fifth Republic}}\n{{Infobox French constituency\n| name                = 3rd Constituency of [[Savoie]]\n| image               = File:MapOfSavoies3rdConstituency.png|thumb|MapOfSavoies3rdConstituency\n| caption             = Savoie's 3rd Constituency shown within [[Savoie]].\n| member-type         = Deputy\n| member              = [[\u00c9milie Bonnivard]] <ref name=\"assemblee-nationale.fr\">{{cite web|url=http://www2.assemblee-nationale.fr/qui|title=577 D\u00e9put\u00e9s - Assembl\u00e9e nationale|website=www2.assemblee-nationale.fr}}</ref>\n| party-colour        = LR\n| member-party        = [[The Republicans (France)|LR]]\n| department          = [[Savoie]]\n| region              = \n| canton              = Aiguebelle, La Chambre, Chamoux-sur-Gelon, Lanslebourg-Mont-Cenis, Modane, Montm\u00e9lian, La Ravoire, La Rochette, Saint-Jean-de-Maurienne, Saint-Michel-de-Maurienne\n| census-date         = 2017\n| Voters              = 72714 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www2.assemblee-nationale.fr/elections/carte/2017/resultats|title=Les r\u00e9sultats aux \u00e9lections l\u00e9gislatives de 2017 - Assembl\u00e9e nationale|website=www2.assemblee-nationale.fr}}</ref>\n}}\n\nThe 3rd constituency of the [[Savoie]] ([[French language|French]]: ''Troisi\u00e8me circonscription de la Savoie'') is a French legislative [[Constituency (France)|constituency]] in the Savoie ''[[Departments of France|d\u00e9partement]]''. Like the other 576 French constituencies, it elects one [[National Assembly of France|MP]] using the [[First-past-the-post voting|first past the post]] election system with a run-off.\n\n==Description==\n\nThe 3rd constituency of [[Savoie]] covers the southern edge of the department along the border of [[France]] and [[Italy]].\n\nThe constituency has fluctuated between centre left and conservative deputies. Boundary changes prior to the [[2012 French legislative election|2012]] have substantially altered the seat, removing the parts of [[Chamb\u00e9ry]] it had previously contained.\n\n==Assembly Members==\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! colspan=2 | Election !! Member !! Party\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Socialist Party (France)/meta/color}}\" | || [[1988 French legislative election|1988]] || [[Roger Rinchet]]||[[Socialist Party (France)|PS]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Rally for the Republic/meta/color}}\" | || [[1993 French legislative election|1993]] || rowspan=\"2\"| [[Michel Bouvard]]||[[Rally for the Republic|RPR]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Union for a Popular Movement/meta/color}}\" | || [[2002 French legislative election|2002]] ||[[Union for a Popular Movement|UMP]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{Socialist Party (France)/meta/color}}\" | || [[2012 French legislative election|2012]] || [[B\u00e9atrice Santais]]||[[Socialist Party (France)|PS]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color: {{The Republicans (France)/meta/color}}\" | || [[2017 French legislative election|2017]] || [[\u00c9milie Bonnivard]]||[[The Republicans (France)|LR]]\n|}\n\n<ref name=\"assemblee-nationale.fr\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n\n{{French National Assembly constituencies}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:French legislative constituencies of Savoie|3]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Constituency of the French Fifth Republic}}\n{{Infobox French constituency\n| name                = 3rd Constituency of [[Savoie]]\n| image               = File:MapOfSavoies3rdConstituency.png|thumb|MapOfSavoies3rdConstituency\n| caption             = Savoie's 3rd Constituency shown within [[Savoie]].\n| member-type         = Deputy\n| member              = [[\u00c9milie Bonnivard]] <ref name=\"assemblee-nationale.fr\">{{cite web|url=http://www2.assemblee-nationale.fr/qui|title=577 D\u00e9put\u00e9s - Assembl\u00e9e nationale|website=www2.assemblee-nationale.fr}}</ref>\n| party-colour        = LR